                                         "brief_info":  "Emzor Paracetamol Syrup is used to relieve mild to moderate pain from a headache, toothache, cold, flu, joint pain.",
                                         "description":  "\u003cp\u003eEmzor Paracetamol Syrup - 60ml is an antipyretic and analgesic for fast relief of pains, feverish conditions, teething pains, cold symptoms and head aches in children.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eThis medicine works by reducing the activity of certain chemicals in the body to provide pain-relieving effects. Emzor Paracetamol is also used to reduce fever. This medicine reduces fever by increasing the loss of heat from the body. Emzor Paracetamol Syrup may also be taken in combination with other medicines to treat certain conditions as recommended by the doctor. Emzor Paracetamol Syrup is used together with Caffeine and Aspirin to relieve the pain associated with a migraine headache. The pain is relieved because the effect of Emzor Paracetamol gets increased when used together with caffeine or aspirin.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredient:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eEach 5ml contains Paracetamo BP 125mg.\u003c/p\u003e",
                                         "how_to_use":  "\u003cp\u003eUp to 1 year: 1/2 teaspoon or 2.5 ml\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e1 to 6 years: 1 teaspoonful or 5ml\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e6 to 12 years: 2 teaspoonful or 10ml\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eDoses may be given every 4 - 6 hours but not more than 4 times in any 24 hours.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e",
                                         "specification":  "\u003cp\u003enull\u003c/p\u003e",
                                         "famasi_advice":  "\u003cp\u003eDo not exceed recommended dose. If symptoms persist after 3 days consult your doctor. Keep all medicines away from the reach of children\u003c/p\u003e",
